title: Week 9 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Bizarro Week - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/8
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode following a strange weekend of football! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 9! Which disappointing performances are actually cause for concern going forward? Plus, injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 8th, 2021.
  
 (08:10) - Monday Punday
 (10:20) - NFL News 
 (21:10) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (22:25) - QB Studs
 (24:15) - RB Studs
 (31:05) - WR Studs
 (38:35) - TE Studs
 (43:00) - Fantasy Duds
 (43:10) - QB Duds
 (52:15) - RB Duds
 (54:50) - WR Duds
 (01:03:40) - TE Duds
